{"type":null,"faqId":14625,"title":"手机无法显示 SIM 卡中的联系人，如何解决？","answer":"<p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\n\">在联系人列表，打开选项菜单，点击<b>要显示的联系人</b>，然后打开<b>显示</b></span><b><span> SIM </span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">卡联系人</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">开关。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:2.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;page-break-after:avoid;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:9.0pt;font-family:'Book Antiqua','serif';position:relative;top:3.0pt;tab-stops:105.0pt\"><span><img width=\"48\" height=\"16\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20140828172248499001.jpg\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:2.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:62.35pt;line-height:10.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:9.0pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span>SIM </span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\n\">卡刚插入手机后，需要一段时间加载联系人，请耐心等待。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;page-break-after:avoid;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span><img width=\"557\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20140828172248470002.gif\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuatio